We all know how important it is to get out and vote next month but do we all know why? Stacey Abrams broke down some very important topics including early voting, first time voting and safely casting your ballot during a Global Pandemic. If you still have questions about voting, check out the entire interview by clicking the link in my bio! #Vote #StateOfInspiration

This is episode ✌🏽 of State of Inspiration!
